# English Only

All content inside this project must be written in English:

- Documentation (README, rules, comments in config files)
- Code comments and docstrings
- Commit messages and PR descriptions
- User-facing error messages and logs
- Variable names, function names, and identifiers (already expected in English)

Do not add Portuguese or other non-English text to the codebase.
